    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Not really \"incidents,\" just a general push for predictability. The regulators are worried about the \"black box\" nature of high-level reasoning. They don't want a car trying to be \"smart\" if it can't explain exactly why it made a move. Safe Mode makes everything transparent. It's just a standard safety move, nothing personal.",
